{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_QC08_HAR_540.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x24,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "...And so, it was a very beautiful place."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Hmm, a ruin where everything was made of glass... That is very interesting."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x15d,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "I would've loved to see it with my own eyes. Oh, how regrettable it is that I couldn't join you..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x15f,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "The key to unlocking the mysteries of the ancient civilization probably lies within there somewhere."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x15f,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "The glass forge still burns, and the glass flowers still bloom..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x160,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "This discovery is beyond amazing!<CR>We have witnessed a historical moment!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1a4,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "I-I'm glad you're happy. And here, this is a souvenir for you."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x18,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "Stop! Ayesha, that won't do.<CR>That just won't do."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x122,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "Wh-What won't do? Don't you like this souvenir?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x22,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "That's not it. That glasswork is a historically and academically important item."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x23,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "Referring to it as a souvenir...<CR>As one who pursues the truth,<CR>that is simply a thoughtless remark."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x23,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "By no means is that a souvenir.<CR>Yes...it is a discovery."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x124,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "I-I'm sorry. I didn't know."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x25,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "Now let's have a do-over, starting from when you finished your report and were about to give me your discovery."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1a4,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "Oh, okay. This stick is a precious discovery. Please accept it."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x1a,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "Uhhh..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x56,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "How splendid! I'd like to praise you highly for your additional use of the term precious."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x57,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "I'll teach you more academically technical terms as we go along."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "(I wonder if discovery is a technical<CR>term...)"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x58,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "And now, this discovery is very interesting. What do you think it is?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "Umm, it looks like an ordinary glass stick to me. It's nothing out of the ordinary..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "msg_string": "Unacceptable. From this single artifact, I was able to understand 80% of their lifestyle."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x122,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "msg_string": "Huh, really!?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x124,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x18,
            "msg_string": "(Maybe he'll know the reason why Nio disappeared, too...)"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x15d,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x19,
            "msg_string": "I'd like you to focus on the pointy end of this stick. Doesn't it remind you of something?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x15f,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1a,
            "msg_string": "Yes. This is, without a doubt, a toothpick. That's something that ancient people used."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1b,
            "msg_string": "A t-toothpick? Even though it's this big?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x161,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1c,
            "msg_string": "That's one of the keys. According to my theory, the ancients had very large bodies."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x15b,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1d,
            "msg_string": "I was never able to concretely nail down their size, but today, it has all become clear."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x15b,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1e,
            "msg_string": "Judging by this toothpick, the ancients were 10 meters tall. That is my conclusion."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x15b,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1f,
            "msg_string": "That is the hypothesis that I have<CR>derived from this landmark discovery.<CR>Do you have any comments?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x20,
            "msg_string": "I-I wonder... I kinda feel like it might be something completely different."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x15c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x21,
            "msg_string": "No, that has to be it. With this shape, it can be nothing else but a toothpick!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x193,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x22,
            "msg_string": "Yes, this is an epoch of discovery. It'll be the key to revealing their ancient civilization!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x23,
            "msg_string": "(Hmm, well, it looks like he's happy with it, so I guess it's okay.)"
        }
    ]
}